title: orxata sound system 1.0 ogg vorbis q7 2007
description:
1.0 is the first album of Orxata Sound System, until now we had been able to listen to a pair of beta versions and a demo.
This is the result of more than two years of work; an album in which different influences within electronic music and valencian folk music come together; electro, dub, drum&bass, ragga, rap, jazz, folk, tecno, dance...
